## PAPERLESS ORDER
February 15th, 2025

Following the Defendant failing to appear before the District Court to answer to criminal charges filed against them, the Court then issued a bench warrant for Failure to Appear. The counsel for the State actxrz then notified the Court that the Defendant has left Clark County as a whole. Therefore counsel for the State then motioned for nolle prosequi to be entered. As such, this Court GRANTS the entry of nolle prosequi. In the matter of [CR-0060-25 - State of Mayflower v. HenryJahan](https://trello.com/c/O73P5Hk7) the Court hereby dismisses this matter without prejudice.

IT IS SO ORDERED

/s/ Hon. Tobyrulles4568
Magistrate Judge
District Court of Clark County
